1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:08,000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

2
00:01:02,540 --> 00:01:04,000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

3
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:07,980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel,
The Eternal Fragrance]

4
00:01:08,020 --> 00:01:11,140
[Episode 3]

5
00:01:12,110 --> 00:01:13,340
If I try to kill her now,

6
00:01:13,910 --> 00:01:15,530
the fox spirit will probably show up to save her.

7
00:01:16,750 --> 00:01:19,650
I'll shatter her meridians while I have the chance.

8
00:01:48,550 --> 00:01:49,810
We've been moved somewhere else?

9
00:01:54,670 --> 00:01:56,090
So we passed the first trial?

10
00:02:07,270 --> 00:02:08,250
Xiaobangchui?

11
00:02:09,870 --> 00:02:10,900
Xiaobangchui!

12
00:02:13,430 --> 00:02:14,370
You guys made it too?

13
00:02:14,670 --> 00:02:15,500
Xiaobangchui!

14
00:02:19,150 --> 00:02:20,410
You guys made it too. That's great!

15
00:02:20,430 --> 00:02:21,220
You're here too.

16
00:02:26,550 --> 00:02:28,740
Xiaobangchui, what happened to your clothes...?

17
00:02:29,320 --> 00:02:30,130
Don't even ask.

18
00:02:30,590 --> 00:02:31,900
It was all icicles and snow blades

19
00:02:31,920 --> 00:02:32,900
along the way.

20
00:02:32,920 --> 00:02:34,220
I'm lucky I didn't get skewered.

21
00:02:36,430 --> 00:02:39,300
Xiuyuan, how are you? Are you hurt?

22
00:02:40,990 --> 00:02:42,220
And it was freezing cold.

23
00:02:42,390 --> 00:02:43,850
I almost didn't make it.

24
00:02:46,710 --> 00:02:47,410
What about you guys?

25
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:49,220
We ran into some kind of mystical formation.

26
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:51,970
But with Ye here,

27
00:02:52,390 --> 00:02:53,370
nothing could stop us.

28
00:02:55,480 --> 00:02:57,570
So we passed the first trial?

29
00:02:59,920 --> 00:03:00,530
Next...

30
00:03:01,590 --> 00:03:03,500
Help! Don't kill me!

31
00:03:08,990 --> 00:03:09,460
You...

32
00:03:17,710 --> 00:03:18,340
Stay back!

33
00:03:19,390 --> 00:03:20,370
Don't kill me!

34
00:03:38,960 --> 00:03:41,940
Tongzhou, is this forest the second trial?

35
00:03:44,270 --> 00:03:45,250
Don't touch anything.

36
00:03:46,990 --> 00:03:48,570
Your Highness, you really are brilliant!

37
00:04:30,470 --> 00:04:31,370
Stop messing around.

38
00:04:31,880 --> 00:04:33,500
Who knows when the second trial will end.

39
00:04:53,640 --> 00:04:54,450
It's miasma.

40
00:04:58,710 --> 00:05:00,010
- What's going on? - What's going on?

41
00:05:00,030 --> 00:05:01,570
- What's happening? - Are you okay?

42
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:15,740
- Changyue! - Changyue!

43
00:05:24,910 --> 00:05:25,420
Changyue!

44
00:05:25,440 --> 00:05:27,500
Don't go out there! Stay in the light.

45
00:05:31,470 --> 00:05:32,210
- Changyue, are you okay?
- Are you okay?

46
00:05:32,230 --> 00:05:32,810
I'm fine.

47
00:05:45,790 --> 00:05:46,620
Tongzhou, what is that?

48
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:47,660
This is bad.

49
00:05:50,710 --> 00:05:51,100
Run!

50
00:05:51,320 --> 00:05:53,060
Where did these wraith birds come from?

51
00:05:53,790 --> 00:05:55,060
They weren't part of the formation.

52
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,420
I was careless.

53
00:05:57,320 --> 00:05:59,570
Didn't expect so many wraiths here.

54
00:06:00,790 --> 00:06:03,570
They must have been disturbed by our formation.

55
00:06:32,710 --> 00:06:33,210
Move!

56
00:06:48,030 --> 00:06:49,450
You little brat.

57
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:50,980
Can't you just run away quietly? What's wrong with you?

58
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:51,770
I'll beat...

59
00:07:33,030 --> 00:07:33,660
Run!

60
00:07:35,390 --> 00:07:36,130
Xiaobangchui!

61
00:07:37,350 --> 00:07:38,180
Lei Xiuyuan!

62
00:07:43,440 --> 00:07:44,690
Why didn't you tell me they were gone?

63
00:07:45,790 --> 00:07:47,620
We were running for our lives just now.

64
00:07:47,640 --> 00:07:48,810
Couldn't care less about anything else.

65
00:07:52,030 --> 00:07:54,860
Tongzhou, this is just a trial.

66
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:56,540
They can't be in real danger.

67
00:07:56,640 --> 00:07:58,130
Your Highness, Lei Xiuyuan

68
00:07:58,150 --> 00:07:59,330
isn't one of us.

69
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:01,860
He's skilled. Maybe he already escaped.

70
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:03,330
Right, Tongzhou.

71
00:08:03,760 --> 00:08:05,180
Let's get out of this creepy forest first.

72
00:08:05,440 --> 00:08:06,250
It's so scary here.

73
00:08:07,640 --> 00:08:08,420
Tongzhou,

74
00:08:08,760 --> 00:08:10,420
let's go first, okay?

75
00:08:15,520 --> 00:08:16,010
Let's go.

76
00:08:23,320 --> 00:08:23,770
Let's go!

77
00:08:28,790 --> 00:08:29,250
Get in!

78
00:08:29,320 --> 00:08:30,330
No, no!

79
00:08:30,910 --> 00:08:32,260
Caves are full of monsters and ghosts.

80
00:08:32,590 --> 00:08:33,090
I'm not going.

81
00:09:00,040 --> 00:09:01,610
This cave seems really deep.

82
00:09:09,350 --> 00:09:10,970
Hope there isn't anything creepy in here.

83
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:18,850
Wind?

84
00:09:19,280 --> 00:09:20,610
So there's an exit here?

85
00:09:22,830 --> 00:09:24,060
We need to get out fast.

86
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:27,020
I don't want to be chased by those crazy birds again.

87
00:09:33,470 --> 00:09:34,060
Um...

88
00:09:36,400 --> 00:09:37,260
you go in first.

89
00:09:57,160 --> 00:09:57,970
What's going on?

90
00:10:00,830 --> 00:10:01,210
Let's go.

91
00:10:03,960 --> 00:10:04,730
It's a dead end!

92
00:10:05,590 --> 00:10:07,060
Why are these creepy things everywhere?

93
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:09,060
Ghost butterflies of the deep valley, feeding on spirits and bones.

94
00:10:09,350 --> 00:10:10,060
They're bone-devouring butterflies.

95
00:10:10,280 --> 00:10:11,420
What a cursed name.

96
00:10:11,750 --> 00:10:12,810
Is this also part of the trial?

97
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:23,810
Block them!

98
00:10:26,920 --> 00:10:27,690
Hang in there.

99
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:29,420
You have plenty of spirit power. You can do this!

100
00:10:32,280 --> 00:10:33,300
Hang in there.

101
00:10:33,510 --> 00:10:34,140
Hold on.

102
00:10:35,680 --> 00:10:36,780
Shall I transfer spirit power to you?

103
00:10:51,320 --> 00:10:51,940
Stop!

104
00:10:53,870 --> 00:10:56,540
I'm sorry, really.

105
00:10:58,230 --> 00:11:00,260
I can't die yet. I still have to save Master...

106
00:11:01,510 --> 00:11:02,210
Master?

107
00:11:02,870 --> 00:11:05,420
This is a life-saving talisman I made

108
00:11:05,630 --> 00:11:06,900
using a century of my cultivation.

109
00:11:07,320 --> 00:11:09,780
Remember, it only works once.

110
00:11:10,750 --> 00:11:13,020
Only use it when you absolutely have to.

111
00:11:15,920 --> 00:11:17,730
Master, don't fail me now.

112
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:39,420
Here.

113
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:45,780
Are you okay?

114
00:11:52,990 --> 00:11:54,810
Is the talisman going to destroy him too?

115
00:11:56,160 --> 00:11:57,330
Wait, you...

116
00:11:57,710 --> 00:11:58,810
What did you put inside me?

117
00:11:59,080 --> 00:12:00,140
You can't die.

118
00:12:00,280 --> 00:12:01,140
Wait, hey!

119
00:12:01,470 --> 00:12:03,300
If you die, I can't answer to His Highness.

120
00:12:05,040 --> 00:12:05,690
What's wrong?

121
00:12:14,920 --> 00:12:15,940
My Lord.

122
00:12:26,750 --> 00:12:27,420
Tongzhou!

123
00:12:28,590 --> 00:12:29,210
Tongzhou?

124
00:12:30,680 --> 00:12:31,850
Once Zhao Mingli finishes scouting,

125
00:12:32,110 --> 00:12:33,140
you go back to the capital with him.

126
00:12:34,110 --> 00:12:35,490
Tongzhou!

127
00:12:36,040 --> 00:12:38,660
Tongzhou, I swear

128
00:12:38,870 --> 00:12:40,730
I didn't mean to hurt Xiaobangchui.

129
00:12:40,990 --> 00:12:41,810
Really.

130
00:12:42,830 --> 00:12:45,140
Having the intent to harm is no different from doing it.

131
00:12:49,440 --> 00:12:49,970
Tongzhou.

132
00:13:38,320 --> 00:13:38,850
Tongzhou.

133
00:13:49,870 --> 00:13:50,450
Are you okay?

134
00:14:15,590 --> 00:14:16,260
Be careful.

135
00:14:17,400 --> 00:14:18,140
Here, sit down.

136
00:14:21,230 --> 00:14:22,260
This isn't a trial.

137
00:14:22,990 --> 00:14:24,300
This is murder!

138
00:14:28,320 --> 00:14:31,690
No, the academy wouldn't kill anyone in the trial.

139
00:14:32,350 --> 00:14:33,420
We almost died.

140
00:14:33,830 --> 00:14:35,420
Why haven't the masters shown up?

141
00:14:42,510 --> 00:14:44,540
What was your deal at the cave entrance last night?

142
00:14:44,560 --> 00:14:45,540
What formation were you setting up?

143
00:15:25,800 --> 00:15:26,660
What are you thinking about?

144
00:15:44,440 --> 00:15:45,260
What are you thinking about?

145
00:15:49,710 --> 00:15:50,300
Don't go.

146
00:15:51,920 --> 00:15:52,660
Don't leave me.

147
00:15:54,800 --> 00:15:55,540
Let go!

148
00:15:57,800 --> 00:15:59,210
You almost got me killed again!

149
00:16:00,080 --> 00:16:01,260
I've got you figured out.

150
00:16:01,590 --> 00:16:03,140
You never change!

151
00:16:03,830 --> 00:16:05,060
I knew it the moment I saw you.

152
00:16:11,110 --> 00:16:14,490
Master once said those with abundant spirit power command natural authority,

153
00:16:14,750 --> 00:16:15,660
and all spirits avoid them.

154
00:16:16,920 --> 00:16:18,780
Could Master's talisman

155
00:16:18,870 --> 00:16:20,330
have boosted his cultivation,

156
00:16:20,750 --> 00:16:21,900
spiking his power

157
00:16:22,470 --> 00:16:24,490
and turning him from a jinx into a bodyguard?

158
00:16:26,750 --> 00:16:27,570
What do you know?

159
00:16:29,350 --> 00:16:30,330
I know

160
00:16:30,750 --> 00:16:32,940
you're naturally gifted, lean, and tall.

161
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:34,690
From now on, I'll...

162
00:16:35,160 --> 00:16:37,020
You'll stick with me. I'll protect you.

163
00:16:41,630 --> 00:16:42,690
Her magic is clearly weak,

164
00:16:43,320 --> 00:16:44,730
yet I keep failing to get her.

165
00:16:45,160 --> 00:16:46,300
I'll have to make a risky move.

166
00:16:46,960 --> 00:16:49,180
You're not saying anything, so that means you agree.

167
00:16:51,350 --> 00:16:52,210
It's settled then!

168
00:16:59,400 --> 00:17:00,090
Not again.

169
00:17:19,920 --> 00:17:20,530
Tongzhou.

170
00:17:30,640 --> 00:17:32,860
Riyan? When did it come out?

171
00:17:34,640 --> 00:17:36,450
No. It's not the real one.

172
00:17:38,880 --> 00:17:40,820
So this is the nine-tailed fox Zhenyunzi was looking for?

173
00:17:45,960 --> 00:17:47,660
Your Highness, you're a genius.

174
00:17:47,920 --> 00:17:49,450
This fox spirit is no match for you.

175
00:17:50,510 --> 00:17:52,860
We'll head off first so we don't get in your way.

176
00:17:53,990 --> 00:17:55,450
- This fox spirit part of the trial to. - Let go.

177
00:17:56,160 --> 00:17:56,940
Let's fight it together.

178
00:17:57,230 --> 00:17:58,940
Go die yourself if you want. Don't drag me into it.

179
00:18:21,990 --> 00:18:23,340
Your Highness, look,

180
00:18:23,470 --> 00:18:24,770
I really can't bear to leave you.

181
00:18:25,070 --> 00:18:26,420
I'll back you up. Let's do this together.

182
00:18:27,550 --> 00:18:29,180
Its power is in its tail. Cut off its tail!

183
00:19:03,790 --> 00:19:04,900
This fox spirit has a strange aura.

184
00:19:04,990 --> 00:19:06,490
Doesn't seem like a thousand-year-old spirit.

185
00:19:24,070 --> 00:19:26,010
One test and we'll know if it's real.

186
00:19:31,710 --> 00:19:32,380
Tongzhou!

187
00:19:33,400 --> 00:19:34,140
Xiaobangchui!

188
00:19:35,790 --> 00:19:37,730
Wait, wait... hold on.

189
00:19:41,790 --> 00:19:45,050
Do you know Riyan?

190
00:19:49,440 --> 00:19:51,010
He's my friend. Also a big white fox.

191
00:19:52,360 --> 00:19:53,450
Wait,

192
00:19:54,550 --> 00:19:55,490
let me finish.

193
00:19:55,790 --> 00:19:56,450
Let me finish.

194
00:20:16,360 --> 00:20:17,860
You scumbag! You used me as bait?

195
00:20:29,440 --> 00:20:30,340
- Xiaobangchui! - Xiuyuan!

196
00:20:56,160 --> 00:20:59,580
Not again. I've seen a belly full of grass,

197
00:21:00,400 --> 00:21:02,010
but never a belly full of fur.

198
00:21:02,990 --> 00:21:03,770
Its demonic energy isn't strong.

199
00:21:05,200 --> 00:21:06,010
Could it be a clone?

200
00:21:12,030 --> 00:21:14,100
Where is the exit?

201
00:21:17,710 --> 00:21:19,820
Hey, wake up.

202
00:21:21,230 --> 00:21:22,970
Are these all your shed hairs?

203
00:21:25,470 --> 00:21:26,420
Are you balding?

204
00:21:27,070 --> 00:21:27,940
You're the one balding!

205
00:21:28,400 --> 00:21:30,720
I've been eating Ganoderma lucidum and herbs for years.

206
00:21:30,720 --> 00:21:31,620
My fur is thick and shiny.

207
00:21:32,120 --> 00:21:33,580
I've only shed a single strand in all these years.

208
00:21:35,790 --> 00:21:36,940
So only one.

209
00:21:38,200 --> 00:21:39,660
Which one is the real one?

210
00:22:06,990 --> 00:22:07,900
Found it.

211
00:22:25,920 --> 00:22:27,140
Fox spirit, reveal yourself!

212
00:22:33,790 --> 00:22:36,380
Who would've thought? Its true form is just a single fox hair.

213
00:22:38,070 --> 00:22:40,180
The fox must be secretly helping her.

214
00:22:40,840 --> 00:22:42,530
Just a single hair has this much power.

215
00:22:43,360 --> 00:22:44,530
If the real nine-tailed fox showed up,

216
00:22:44,550 --> 00:22:45,620
wouldn't it be unstoppable?

217
00:22:54,070 --> 00:22:55,970
Though it was just an illusionary spirit,

218
00:22:56,230 --> 00:22:58,450
you two actually forced it back to its true form.

219
00:22:59,230 --> 00:23:01,900
You both have impressive skills.

220
00:23:02,960 --> 00:23:04,900
How did you do it?

221
00:23:05,790 --> 00:23:08,100
All thanks to Your Highness's Luminescent Ring.

222
00:23:08,270 --> 00:23:09,620
Otherwise, we'd all be done for.

223
00:23:10,400 --> 00:23:11,940
The Luminescent Ring can ward off evil,

224
00:23:12,310 --> 00:23:13,450
but it can't destroy spirits.

225
00:23:15,030 --> 00:23:15,450
Whatever.

226
00:23:15,470 --> 00:23:18,290
Anyway, you faced danger without fear

227
00:23:18,310 --> 00:23:20,340
and didn't abandon your companions.

228
00:23:20,680 --> 00:23:21,820
That deserves praise.

229
00:23:22,230 --> 00:23:24,580
I hope that once you step onto the immortal path,

230
00:23:24,920 --> 00:23:26,010
you'll keep

231
00:23:26,310 --> 00:23:28,420
this pure heart,

232
00:23:28,600 --> 00:23:31,250
support each other, and fight together.

233
00:23:34,990 --> 00:23:36,660
Sir, does that mean

234
00:23:37,200 --> 00:23:38,210
we all passed?

235
00:23:46,200 --> 00:23:49,420
All candidates present have passed the trial.

236
00:23:54,360 --> 00:23:56,290
You're amazing, Xiaobangchui!

237
00:24:02,920 --> 00:24:04,180
Awesome!

238
00:24:04,880 --> 00:24:07,450
- We passed! - You're incredible, Xiaobangchui!

239
00:24:18,680 --> 00:24:19,340
Lei Xiuyuan,

240
00:24:19,920 --> 00:24:21,660
I didn't think you'd actually get into the academy.

241
00:24:22,310 --> 00:24:23,450
I underestimated you.

242
00:24:24,030 --> 00:24:24,970
How's Shanhua?

243
00:24:25,310 --> 00:24:27,450
[Mo Chen, Xingzheng Hall]
Not dead yet. But close.

244
00:24:28,400 --> 00:24:30,770
Elder Zhenyun wants you to act quickly.

245
00:24:31,120 --> 00:24:33,140
Otherwise, once she enters the academy,

246
00:24:33,270 --> 00:24:34,820
you might have to go in too.

247
00:24:35,270 --> 00:24:38,100
Shanhua's life hangs by a thread. I'm not in the mood to enter the academy.

248
00:24:40,400 --> 00:24:42,820
That depends on how fast you move.

249
00:24:45,120 --> 00:24:46,100
Isn't there a way to capture

250
00:24:47,160 --> 00:24:48,380
the fox spirit without killing the host?

251
00:24:50,310 --> 00:24:51,660
You've only been together for a few days.

252
00:24:52,120 --> 00:24:53,450
Can't bring yourself to do it already?

253
00:24:55,400 --> 00:24:57,450
The fox spirit is powerful and is protective of its master.

254
00:24:58,230 --> 00:24:58,970
I can't beat it.

255
00:25:00,840 --> 00:25:03,380
Elder Zhenyun anticipated that.

256
00:25:15,680 --> 00:25:16,420
What's this?

257
00:25:16,680 --> 00:25:19,770
Soul-destroying Threads. It can bind the primordial spirit of a monster.

258
00:25:20,120 --> 00:25:22,380
But it'll backfire and destroy your soul meridians.

259
00:25:23,550 --> 00:25:24,100
You...

260
00:25:24,710 --> 00:25:27,290
All masters of the immortal sects cut off worldly ties

261
00:25:27,640 --> 00:25:28,690
and pursue the path of detachment.

262
00:25:30,470 --> 00:25:33,140
Do you think Elder Zhenyun would sacrifice his own cultivation

263
00:25:33,400 --> 00:25:34,380
for an outcast

264
00:25:34,960 --> 00:25:37,180
and let you hinder his path to immortality?

265
00:25:40,310 --> 00:25:40,940
Remember,

266
00:25:41,440 --> 00:25:43,770
Lu Shanhua's life is in your hands.

267
00:25:44,270 --> 00:25:46,100
Send the fox spirit to Xingzheng Hall,

268
00:25:46,510 --> 00:25:48,180
and you'll see your brother sooner.

269
00:25:48,600 --> 00:25:49,250
Otherwise,

270
00:25:50,070 --> 00:25:52,730
you'll only reunite in the underworld.

271
00:25:56,070 --> 00:25:57,450
So that's how it is.

272
00:26:04,470 --> 00:26:08,490
Xiaobangchui. Xiaobangchui?

273
00:26:10,920 --> 00:26:13,380
Watching the moon? You're lovesick or something?

274
00:26:14,750 --> 00:26:16,380
Little Matchmaker, I was just looking for you.

275
00:26:17,440 --> 00:26:19,100
Who are you looking for this time?

276
00:26:19,680 --> 00:26:21,490
Not looking for someone. I'm keeping tabs on someone.

277
00:26:21,990 --> 00:26:24,770
On who? That troublemaker?

278
00:26:25,790 --> 00:26:27,250
I think he's got his eye on Riyan.

279
00:26:28,790 --> 00:26:30,140
We definitely need to look into this.

280
00:26:30,680 --> 00:26:33,690
Can't just let that stinky fox end up as a scarf.

281
00:26:38,160 --> 00:26:39,530
Help!

282
00:27:05,470 --> 00:27:08,100
Dual souls entangled, sharing one fate of life and death?

283
00:27:10,120 --> 00:27:10,900
What's going on?

284
00:27:11,790 --> 00:27:13,820
That troublemaker is after you. I'm out!

285
00:27:16,960 --> 00:27:17,450
Hey,

286
00:27:18,030 --> 00:27:19,140
is that something a friend would do?

287
00:27:19,990 --> 00:27:21,010
Will it ever end?

288
00:27:38,550 --> 00:27:39,180
Your Highness.

289
00:27:41,840 --> 00:27:42,580
Prince Ying,

290
00:27:43,600 --> 00:27:45,530
you keep giving me a hard time.

291
00:27:46,070 --> 00:27:48,420
Are you determined to go against Longming Sanctuary?

292
00:27:49,510 --> 00:27:51,940
Is the Yue State trying to become the next Gaolu?

293
00:27:52,230 --> 00:27:53,620
You dare threaten me?

294
00:27:54,030 --> 00:27:56,520
I heard that Elder Xuanshan of Xingzheng Hall is struggling to recover

295
00:27:56,520 --> 00:27:57,490
from his old injuries.

296
00:27:58,550 --> 00:28:00,730
If something happens to him,

297
00:28:01,600 --> 00:28:04,450
who will protect Yue?

298
00:28:06,030 --> 00:28:07,940
You slander my country! That's a capital offense!

299
00:28:17,070 --> 00:28:18,100
Xiaobangchui, the Luminescent Ring!

300
00:28:54,960 --> 00:28:57,100
Burned... burned to ashes?

301
00:28:59,710 --> 00:29:00,620
First time killing?

302
00:29:03,640 --> 00:29:06,380
Don't be scared. You've removed a threat for Yue.

303
00:29:06,790 --> 00:29:07,380
I'll

304
00:29:08,790 --> 00:29:09,940
treat you well from now on.

305
00:29:13,160 --> 00:29:14,290
You just killed people randomly!

306
00:29:14,510 --> 00:29:15,690
Got ground to dust, huh?

307
00:29:16,310 --> 00:29:19,210
That's karma. Justice served!

308
00:29:29,440 --> 00:29:31,100
Is that a divine deer from heaven?

309
00:29:35,510 --> 00:29:38,100
That's a rainbow deer. You've never seen one?

310
00:29:38,550 --> 00:29:39,940
Making such a fuss.

311
00:29:40,550 --> 00:29:41,490
You've seen one?

312
00:29:42,640 --> 00:29:43,660
Of course.

313
00:29:44,070 --> 00:29:45,250
You definitely haven't.

314
00:29:45,600 --> 00:29:46,660
I had one at home when I was little!

315
00:29:46,880 --> 00:29:47,580
You're just acting tough.

316
00:29:48,600 --> 00:29:49,450
Tongzhou!

317
00:29:52,070 --> 00:29:53,180
Is one carriage

318
00:29:53,550 --> 00:29:55,290
enough for all of us?

319
00:29:56,400 --> 00:29:57,210
Time to go grab a seat.

320
00:30:05,470 --> 00:30:07,770
Ambergris? Must be rich.

321
00:30:14,470 --> 00:30:15,620
Little brat.

322
00:30:17,070 --> 00:30:18,050
Your Highness, this way.

323
00:30:28,550 --> 00:30:29,340
Have a seat.

324
00:30:30,640 --> 00:30:31,140
Right here.

325
00:30:31,400 --> 00:30:31,820
Okay.

326
00:30:42,120 --> 00:30:43,730
Where did you go after drinking last night?

327
00:30:45,070 --> 00:30:46,690
I was drunk. Slept at the inn.

328
00:30:56,270 --> 00:30:57,050
We're flying!

329
00:31:12,200 --> 00:31:13,760
♪All the way♪

330
00:31:14,200 --> 00:31:16,280
♪From the foot of the mountain to the peak♪

331
00:31:16,700 --> 00:31:19,000
♪I've passed through cliffs of blades and seas of fire♪

332
00:31:19,560 --> 00:31:22,120
♪Breaking the seal against thousands, returning in glory♪

333
00:31:23,000 --> 00:31:23,960
♪The ones who make it are the chosen ones♪

334
00:31:23,960 --> 00:31:24,530
Alright.

335
00:31:25,120 --> 00:31:25,730
What are you doing?

336
00:31:26,200 --> 00:31:26,900
What are you doing?

337
00:31:26,900 --> 00:31:27,840
♪With you, beneath the stars, the sun and moon♪

338
00:31:27,840 --> 00:31:29,420
- Just let me see. - Xiaobangchui.

339
00:31:29,420 --> 00:31:31,600
♪This unquenchable fervor is a wonder to behold♪

340
00:31:31,790 --> 00:31:32,580
Come over here to look.

341
00:31:32,580 --> 00:31:34,840
♪One final battle, we charge ahead♪

342
00:31:35,160 --> 00:31:35,970
Thanks, Your Highness.

343
00:31:35,970 --> 00:31:38,600
♪The path of light is not far away♪

344
00:31:39,230 --> 00:31:42,340
So many islands. It's beautiful!

345
00:31:52,230 --> 00:31:54,010
This is stunning.

346
00:31:55,230 --> 00:31:56,380
I've never seen anything like it.

347
00:32:03,470 --> 00:32:04,730
Help!

348
00:32:06,550 --> 00:32:07,250
Xiaobangchui!

349
00:32:07,600 --> 00:32:08,250
Xiaobangchui!

350
00:32:08,270 --> 00:32:09,490
What are you doing, Lanya?

351
00:32:09,510 --> 00:32:10,660
Help!

352
00:32:18,120 --> 00:32:18,940
Help!

353
00:32:23,920 --> 00:32:24,530
Hold on tight.

354
00:32:48,000 --> 00:32:50,000
[Mo Yanfan, Chufeng Academy]

355
00:32:56,550 --> 00:32:57,580
I'm a master from the academy.

356
00:32:58,600 --> 00:32:59,860
Are you the freshmen of this year?

357
00:33:01,070 --> 00:33:03,340
Hello, master. I'm Xiaobangchui.

358
00:33:03,680 --> 00:33:06,690
Xiaobangchui? What an interesting name.

359
00:33:07,880 --> 00:33:08,730
And this is...?

360
00:33:10,600 --> 00:33:11,490
I'm Lei Xiuyuan.

361
00:33:12,360 --> 00:33:15,010
Lei Xiuyuan? You're talented.

362
00:33:15,960 --> 00:33:16,860
And you have good character.

363
00:33:19,550 --> 00:33:22,210
The academy is just ahead. Stay steady.

364
00:33:36,640 --> 00:33:37,420
Excuse me.

365
00:33:41,970 --> 00:33:45,200
[Chufeng Academy]

366
00:34:24,920 --> 00:34:25,530
Xiaobangchui!

367
00:34:28,720 --> 00:34:29,300
Are you okay?

368
00:34:29,590 --> 00:34:30,090
I'm fine.

369
00:34:36,760 --> 00:34:37,380
Thanks.

370
00:34:56,070 --> 00:34:56,610
Make way.

371
00:34:57,440 --> 00:34:58,300
- Move aside. - Move aside.

372
00:35:00,630 --> 00:35:01,740
Situ Lanya.

373
00:35:03,150 --> 00:35:04,650
Did you push Xiaobangchui down on purpose?

374
00:35:06,590 --> 00:35:07,900
Yes, I did. So what?

375
00:35:09,720 --> 00:35:11,050
You're going too far!

376
00:35:12,070 --> 00:35:13,130
- Mind your tone! - What did you say?

377
00:35:13,150 --> 00:35:13,900
- Say that again. - You!

378
00:35:13,920 --> 00:35:14,740
- Tongzhou... - What are you doing?

379
00:35:19,440 --> 00:35:21,130
The rules of Chufeng Academy

380
00:35:21,670 --> 00:35:24,650
forbid private fights among disciples.

381
00:35:25,240 --> 00:35:29,530
Anyone who harms a fellow disciple will have their spirit roots destroyed

382
00:35:29,720 --> 00:35:30,610
and be expelled.

383
00:35:30,760 --> 00:35:31,300
But...

384
00:35:34,550 --> 00:35:35,740
There'll be plenty of time.

385
00:35:37,550 --> 00:35:38,380
It's an academy, after all.

386
00:35:38,990 --> 00:35:39,570
Exactly.

387
00:35:42,920 --> 00:35:43,700
Yes, master.

388
00:35:49,110 --> 00:35:50,300
Xiuyuan jumped down after you

389
00:35:50,320 --> 00:35:51,260
without a second thought.

390
00:35:52,190 --> 00:35:53,820
Since when did you two get so close?

391
00:35:55,920 --> 00:35:57,450
He owes me. Guess he's giving himself to me.

392
00:36:05,150 --> 00:36:06,970
Welcome to Chufeng Academy.

393
00:36:07,510 --> 00:36:09,940
The dean and masters are waiting at Hongyang Hall.

394
00:36:10,720 --> 00:36:12,820
Follow me.

395
00:36:13,670 --> 00:36:14,090
Let's go.

396
00:36:15,670 --> 00:36:16,130
Let's go.

397
00:36:28,280 --> 00:36:33,380
No learning, no broadening of talent; no will, no success in studies.

398
00:36:34,510 --> 00:36:37,530
Though you were the most outstanding

399
00:36:37,550 --> 00:36:39,490
among the various sects across the lands,

400
00:36:40,440 --> 00:36:43,450
from the moment you step into Chufeng Academy,

401
00:36:43,800 --> 00:36:45,610
you become its disciple.

402
00:36:46,030 --> 00:36:49,130
You must leave mortal affairs behind,

403
00:36:49,670 --> 00:36:51,560
[Zuo Qiu, Chufeng Academy]
focus on your cultivation,

404
00:36:51,560 --> 00:36:52,570
and strive with diligence.

405
00:36:57,720 --> 00:36:59,010
The path of cultivation

406
00:37:00,440 --> 00:37:02,220
requires a dedicated heart.

407
00:37:05,920 --> 00:37:07,260
What is a dedicated heart?

408
00:37:07,960 --> 00:37:10,300
It could be for a personal wish,

409
00:37:11,110 --> 00:37:14,420
or for the greater good. Neither is better or worse.

410
00:37:14,990 --> 00:37:18,840
But you must know good from evil, distinguish right from wrong,

411
00:37:18,840 --> 00:37:19,900
and cultivate your inner mind.

412
00:37:21,510 --> 00:37:24,530
I heard Dean Zuo Qiu is a thousand years old.

413
00:37:26,320 --> 00:37:27,940
What elixir of immortality is he on?

414
00:37:27,960 --> 00:37:28,800
[Lin You, Chufeng Academy]

415
00:37:31,070 --> 00:37:34,050
The path of cultivation is long. Remember this always.

416
00:37:34,550 --> 00:37:37,820
Never forget your original intent along the way.

417
00:37:40,280 --> 00:37:41,090
Yes!

418
00:37:45,440 --> 00:37:48,860
Alright, go get settled in.

419
00:37:55,070 --> 00:37:55,970
- Let's go. - Go.

420
00:37:57,720 --> 00:37:58,450
Xiaobangchui.

421
00:38:00,960 --> 00:38:01,820
You stay.

422
00:38:09,670 --> 00:38:10,420
You guys go ahead.

423
00:38:24,880 --> 00:38:25,650
Lei Xiuyuan?

424
00:38:30,550 --> 00:38:31,530
You're waiting for Xiaobangchui?

425
00:38:33,400 --> 00:38:34,090
You're overthinking it.

426
00:38:38,110 --> 00:38:40,970
You said you didn't want to enter the academy.

427
00:38:41,990 --> 00:38:43,420
Why the sudden change of heart?

428
00:38:44,800 --> 00:38:45,570
None of your business.

429
00:38:49,240 --> 00:38:50,420
It's because of your brother, isn't it?

430
00:38:52,760 --> 00:38:54,050
His name is Lu Shanhua.

431
00:39:06,510 --> 00:39:07,340
What do you know?

432
00:39:12,960 --> 00:39:14,300
I ran into Senior Mo Chen,

433
00:39:14,880 --> 00:39:15,610
so I know a bit about it.

434
00:39:16,360 --> 00:39:17,530
My uncle Xuanshanzi

435
00:39:17,550 --> 00:39:18,610
is one of the two chief elders

436
00:39:18,630 --> 00:39:19,900
of Xingzheng Hall.

437
00:39:20,190 --> 00:39:20,940
If you need...

438
00:39:21,880 --> 00:39:22,380
I don't need it.

439
00:39:22,920 --> 00:39:23,420
Why?

440
00:39:28,550 --> 00:39:29,820
As a member of the Gaolu imperial family,

441
00:39:30,960 --> 00:39:32,130
haven't you thought about revenge?

442
00:39:33,070 --> 00:39:33,940
Don't you want to restore Gaolu?

443
00:39:38,240 --> 00:39:39,130
Gaolu is long gone.

444
00:39:42,960 --> 00:39:44,130
I won't be a puppet in the conflict

445
00:39:44,720 --> 00:39:45,940
between Yue and Wugou.

446
00:39:48,670 --> 00:39:49,570
Save your schemes.

447
00:39:52,840 --> 00:39:54,090
Xiaobangchui is clever.

448
00:39:54,630 --> 00:39:56,010
She's definitely noticed you scheming

449
00:39:56,400 --> 00:39:57,260
to get close to her.

450
00:40:07,670 --> 00:40:10,340
Sir, have you really never seen my senior brother?

451
00:40:12,150 --> 00:40:13,420
I really haven't.

452
00:40:18,190 --> 00:40:21,220
Your master sent you here,

453
00:40:21,840 --> 00:40:23,970
which means he believed you were destined for this academy.

454
00:40:24,280 --> 00:40:26,530
And the fact that Immortal Dongyang gave you those beads

455
00:40:27,550 --> 00:40:29,170
proves you have an immortal affinity.

456
00:40:30,400 --> 00:40:32,010
Just stay here with peace of mind.

457
00:40:32,320 --> 00:40:33,650
Work hard on your cultivation,

458
00:40:34,030 --> 00:40:35,090
and everything you seek

459
00:40:35,800 --> 00:40:37,420
will fall into place.

460
00:40:39,070 --> 00:40:40,820
When will that be?

461
00:40:41,720 --> 00:40:42,940
I can't even find Senior Brother.

462
00:40:43,840 --> 00:40:45,130
How am I supposed to find Master?

463
00:40:53,150 --> 00:40:53,700
Sir,

464
00:40:54,880 --> 00:40:56,090
are you trying to send me away?

465
00:40:57,030 --> 00:40:58,820
No.

466
00:40:59,280 --> 00:41:01,570
I'd like to give you a formal name.

467
00:41:02,150 --> 00:41:03,010
Would you like that?

468
00:41:04,400 --> 00:41:06,010
Can't "Xiaobangchui" be my formal name?

469
00:41:09,840 --> 00:41:11,050
Your master

470
00:41:11,400 --> 00:41:12,740
just loves cutting corners.

471
00:41:14,070 --> 00:41:17,860
"Xiaobangchui" is really just a nickname.

472
00:41:18,440 --> 00:41:20,050
Since he sent you here,

473
00:41:20,280 --> 00:41:21,610
I might as well be your second master.

474
00:41:22,190 --> 00:41:23,610
So I'll give you a formal name.

475
00:41:23,880 --> 00:41:25,340
Your master would be happy

476
00:41:25,670 --> 00:41:26,820
about it.

477
00:41:28,800 --> 00:41:31,130
That old geezer really did cut corners.

478
00:41:34,320 --> 00:41:35,420
Sir, please give me a new name.

479
00:41:38,630 --> 00:41:40,420
You were raised by your master.

480
00:41:40,840 --> 00:41:42,380
And you're a girl.

481
00:41:42,590 --> 00:41:43,300
Your surname will be Jiang.

482
00:41:44,070 --> 00:41:45,050
As you said,

483
00:41:45,190 --> 00:41:48,450
your master found you

484
00:41:48,590 --> 00:41:50,740
by the river at first light.

485
00:41:51,320 --> 00:41:53,780
The first light of day is dawn.

486
00:41:54,960 --> 00:41:57,420
You could be called Jiang Li.

487
00:41:58,150 --> 00:41:59,420
Jiang Li?

488
00:42:00,440 --> 00:42:01,610
But "Jiang Li" sounds like

489
00:42:02,030 --> 00:42:03,130
"about to leave."

490
00:42:03,880 --> 00:42:05,650
Since you hope to find your master,

491
00:42:05,800 --> 00:42:07,090
you mustn't leave.

492
00:42:11,240 --> 00:42:12,340
"Fei" means

493
00:42:13,280 --> 00:42:14,380
"not."

494
00:42:18,110 --> 00:42:18,860
Xiaobangchui.

495
00:42:19,670 --> 00:42:20,650
Starting today,

496
00:42:21,070 --> 00:42:21,970
your name is

497
00:42:22,360 --> 00:42:23,970
Jiang Lifei.

498
00:42:32,960 --> 00:42:33,570
Jiang

499
00:42:34,280 --> 00:42:34,970
Li

500
00:42:35,990 --> 00:42:36,610
Fei?

501
00:42:38,020 --> 00:42:39,000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

502
00:42:39,000 --> 00:42:40,760
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel,
The Eternal Fragrance]

503
00:42:42,480 --> 00:42:45,380
♪If legends tell of a perilous land♪

504
00:42:45,540 --> 00:42:48,300
♪Why not give it a shot and march with all my might?♪

505
00:42:48,420 --> 00:42:50,940
♪Fearless through a hundred battles, I finally earn my place♪

506
00:42:51,100 --> 00:42:53,140
♪Happy new semester♪

507
00:42:53,300 --> 00:42:55,900
♪Wearing a flowing green robe, like immortal feathers dancing♪

508
00:42:55,980 --> 00:42:58,660
♪The fierce gale is grasped tightly in my palm♪

509
00:42:58,900 --> 00:43:01,340
♪Hearts united, drawing together for a thunderous strike♪

510
00:43:01,540 --> 00:43:03,620
♪Refusing to coast through life♪

511
00:43:03,740 --> 00:43:06,140
♪Though a crisis is sealed before us, I will not give up♪

512
00:43:06,260 --> 00:43:08,980
♪Leaving my silhouette between heaven and earth♪

513
00:43:09,420 --> 00:43:11,940
♪Just as I hesitate and drift away♪

514
00:43:12,100 --> 00:43:13,900
♪A sudden awakening comes♪

515
00:43:14,060 --> 00:43:16,860
♪We will make all the world's pain kneel before us♪

516
00:43:16,980 --> 00:43:19,380
♪The song of victory never stops♪

517
00:43:19,540 --> 00:43:21,700
♪The darkness all turns into illusions♪

518
00:43:21,780 --> 00:43:24,220
♪Unmatched across the Three Realms♪

519
00:43:24,300 --> 00:43:27,260
♪With bare hands, we clench our fists tight♪

520
00:43:27,460 --> 00:43:30,020
♪Soaring high against the wind to hunt the enemy♪

521
00:43:30,180 --> 00:43:34,620
♪Together we shatter the filth and malice of this world♪

522
00:43:34,740 --> 00:43:37,700
♪Guarding our ground, we rise to the peak♪

523
00:43:37,940 --> 00:43:40,340
♪No need to wait around for natural gifts♪

524
00:43:40,500 --> 00:43:43,260
♪Learning knows no end; we unite as one♪

525
00:43:43,260 --> 00:43:45,980
♪The howling wind obeys my command♪

526
